OL,7,FA long-awaited report into the
OL,8,Factivities of Stakeknife ` the Army's
OL,9,Ftop agent in Northern Ireland during
OL,10,Fthe Troubles ` will be published on
OL,11,FMarch 8, the PSNI has confirmed.
OL,13,FTemporary deputy chief constable Chris
OL,14,FTodd said police and the Public
OL,15,FProsecution Service (PPS) have had to
OL,16,Fsatisfy themselves that the report
OL,17,Fwill not prejudice any ongoing
OL,18,Finvestigations ahead of publication.
