OL,3,CReport into activities of Stakeknife
OL,4,Cto be published in March, police
OL,5,Cconfirm
OL,7,FStakeknife worked within the IRA's
OL,8,Fnotorious "nutting squad",
OL,9,Finterrogating suspected informers
OL,10,Fduring the Troubles.
OL,12,FHis alleged activities were
OL,13,Finvestigated as part of Kenova, which
OL,14,Fexamined crimes such as murder and
OL,15,Ftorture and the role played by the
OL,16,Fsecurity services, including MI5.
OL,18,FStakeknife was widely believed to be
OL,19,FWest Belfast man Freddie Scappaticci,
OL,20,Fwho was in his 70s when he died last
OL,21,Fyear.
