OL,7,FThe report was handed over to the PSNI
OL,8,Flast year.
OL,10,FIt was authored by Jon Boutcher but he
OL,11,Fhas since taken up position as PSNI
OL,12,Fchief constable and has recused
OL,13,Fhimself from involvement in its
OL,14,Fpublication.
OL,16,FFormer chief constable of Police
OL,17,FScotland Sir Iain Livingstone replaced
OL,18,FMr Boutcher as head of Operation
OL,19,FKenova.
