OL,7,FAnswering a question at a public
OL,8,Fmeeting of the Policing Board, Mr Todd
OL,9,Fsaid: "You will be aware that the
OL,10,Freport has been written, it sits with
OL,11,Fus, we've confirmed before there's no
OL,12,Fchanges or redactions to that report.
OL,14,F"It is as authored as an independent
OL,15,Freport."
OL,17,FThe senior officer said responsibility
OL,18,Fsat with himself to decide when it
OL,19,Fwould be published.
